00:45:10.040 --> 00:45:13.260
If more products are added. then
q is going to be greater

00:45:13.260 --> 00:45:17.730
than k momentarily, and you
would shift toward reactants,

00:45:17.730 --> 00:45:25.480
shift toward the left, and
again, we saw that down there.

